description: Omai Gold Mines Corp. explores for and develops base and precious metals. It holds a 100% interest in the Omai prospecting license that covers an area of 4,590 acres, including the past-producing Omai Gold mine located in the Potaro mining district of Guyana, as well as adjoining eastern flats mining permits. The company is based in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Ms. Elaine  Ellingham B.Sc., M.B.A., M.Sc., MBA, P.Geo.
